        <div id="how-to-use" class="window-height not-title">
                <h2>
                    Instructions for using 
                    <span style="color: #841934; font-family:'Brittany Signature Regular'">Gyne</span>
                    <span style="color: #ef6ebb;font-family:'Brittany Signature Regular'">Connect</span> 
                </h2>
                <br>
            <p>
                To find a gynecologist in your city, go to the <b><span style="color: #841934;">Find a gynecologist </span></b>tab, enter your city, and choose the most suitable doctor for you. <br/>
                To help you make the best decision, we have provided a variety of <b>tags, information and reviews</b> of each of the doctors.<br/>
                To submit a review, go to the <b><span style="color: #841934;">Review </span></b>tab. We encourage you to provide feedback for each of the appointments
                you have made, so the reviews remain as accurate as possible. We sincerely request you to <b>only</b> fill this form if you have actually consulted with the doctor.<br/>
                For an online consultation, you can book an appointment with one of the doctors who have registered on the website for a 
                small fee (or for free for some doctors!) in one of the available time slots. However, it is strongly recommend you to use 
                this service only in case of <b>emergencies</b>, as the physical examination would provide more accurate results. <br/>
                If you find any discrepancies for any doctor listed here, fill the <b><span style="color: #841934;">Report</span></b> form so that it can be rectified.
                <br/><br/>
                <span style="color: #841934; font-family:'Brittany Signature Regular'">For Gynecologists:</span><br/>
                If you consider yourself to be one of the <b>trustworthy, respectful, non-judgemental</b> doctors here, please register on the 
                <b><span style="color: #841934;">Sign up as a doctor</span></b> page.<br/>
                You will be asked to enter some details, after which you will be thoroughly <b>verified</b>. 
                Once verified, your account will be created and you will receive an email, after which you can consult patients for a fee of your choosing at your preferred timings.
            </p>
